node.text: My RTK praise break for today 🔥🔥🔥 y’all get up and dance. Jump out of that bed of depression and fear and move!! Y’all think I just praise break once a day???? NOPE!!! I got so much to thank God for! How bout you? Got my dance on at the closing of our service today at @mylimitlesschurch y’all I think I shocked myself when I two stepped 😂my daddy would be so proud at my Dancing feet. 😂😂 I dismissed the service and pulled out an oldie, my church never wants to leave lol I love it!! Such a powerful series “Catfished” I’m doing right now. Catch the replay of my sermon “Access Denied” on my YouTube channel. Search Real Talk Kim or click the link in my bio. #WeAreLimitless #LimitlessLove #SundaysAtLimitless #realtalkkkim

node.text:
We often talk about the woman with the issue of blood's HEALING miracle, but not her OTHER miracle. She lost blood for 12 years and remained ALIVE. THAT IS A MIRACLE! Some of you are dealing with issues in your body right now. On your road to recovery PRAISE God for sustaining you! Your miracle is already in the making! 

“A woman in the crowd had suffered for twelve years with constant bleeding, and she could find no cure. Coming up behind Jesus, she touched the fringe of his robe. Immediately, the bleeding stopped. “Who touched me?” Jesus asked. Everyone denied it, and Peter said, “Master, this whole crowd is pressing up against you.” But Jesus said, “Someone deliberately touched me, for I felt healing power go out from me.” When the woman realized that she could not stay hidden, she began to tremble and fell to her knees in front of him. The whole crowd heard her explain why she had touched him and that she had been immediately healed. “Daughter,” he said to her, “your faith has made you well. Go in peace.””
‭‭Luke‬ ‭8:43-48‬ ‭NLT‬‬
